                     <interp inst="t18300415-354-person2939" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was in Smithfield on Monday morning, the 15th of March; I saw the prisoner and two other boys following this gentleman - I got as close as I could, and saw the prisoner draw the handkerchief from this gentleman's pocket, and pass it to another <rs id="t18300415-354-deflabel1919" type="occupation">boy</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-354-defend2935 t18300415-354-deflabel1919"></join>, who got away; I took the prisoner, and got him through the crowd - I told the prosecutor of it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going through Smithfield, and this gentleman accused me of robbing a person of his handkerchief; I knew nothing of it.</p>
